EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   14 THRU 17 JUN WITHIN 43 MILES OF
   57-54.9N 009-57.9W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 172000Z JUN.
